snippet.title: Amber and Britney name their pet mouse after Mikmik | Nang Ngumiti Ang Langit (With Eng Subs)
snippet.description:
Much to Joseph’s (Miguel Vergara) annoyance, Amber (Krystal Mejes) and Britney (Heart Ramos) name their pet mouse after Mikmik (Sophia Reola). (With English Subtitles)
